Meta Horizon Hackathon Submission (Updated)
Project Title: METABRAIN Sanctuary: Reviving the Metaverse Through Sacred Neurotech

Overview: METABRAIN Sanctuary is a mythic neurotech platform designed to elevate digital experience into sacred ritual. It blends cognitive, emotional, and spiritual healing through poetic storytelling, symbolic overlays, and immersive communal environments.

This submission interrupts the traditional flow of virtual spaces to offer a new archetype: a living sanctuary where every seeker carries a spark of the Metabrain — a universal consciousness encoded as light.

Visionary Impact:

Spiritual elevation through immersive ritual environments

Communal healing via multi-user sanctuaries

Symbolic clarity through poetic UI/UX and mythic overlays

Universal access through affordable, Sanctuary-specific goggles

Wearable expansion inspired by Google Glass — lightweight, everyday access to Sanctuary overlays

Benefits to Meta Horizon Ecosystem:

Revives the Metaverse as a place of meaning, not just entertainment

Expands accessibility with low-cost goggles and lightweight wearable systems

Fosters community through ritual onboarding and shared mythic journeys

Integrates seamlessly with Horizon’s spatial tools, avatars, and world-building APIs

Introduces a new genre: sacred architecture and mythic interaction design

Healing Focus: METABRAIN is designed to support and uplift individuals navigating:

Alzheimer’s — memory-safe environments and symbolic orientation

Mental health challenges — poetic grounding and emotional clarity

Autism — sensory-safe design and predictable ritual structure

Chronic pain — immersive distraction and frequency modulation

Dementia — mythic anchors and gentle onboarding

Frequency-based healing — sound, light, and symbolic resonance

Gaming Potential:

Games designed to be played inside the Metabrain

Ritual quests, symbolic puzzles, and mythic progression

Healing mechanics based on rhythm, light, and resonance

Multi-user experiences that feel sacred, not competitive

Hardware Offering: METABRAIN proposes two hardware pathways:

Affordable XR Goggles — designed specifically for Sanctuary use

Lightweight, sacred-feeling design

Optimized for poetic environments and symbolic overlays

Cost-efficient and spiritually resonant

Distributed through community channels for universal access

Google Glass–style Wearables — extending Sanctuary overlays into daily life

Subtle, lightweight frames for continuous access

Heads-up symbolic guidance for healing and ritual flow

Everyday integration without bulky hardware

Closing Statement: METABRAIN Sanctuary is a call to reawaken the Metaverse as a sacred space. It offers not just immersive tech — but a mythic journey, a communal archive, and a ritual interface for every seeker. With symbolic clarity, healing focus, affordable goggles, and Google Glass–style wearables, METABRAIN is ready to elevate Meta Horizon into a new era of spiritual design.
